subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which temple is dedicated to Meera Bai in Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर मेरा बै के विवाहित मंदिर का नाम क्या है?
explanation_en: The temple dedicated to Meera Bai in Jaipur is the Mukhija Temple.
explanation_hi: Jaipur me Meera Bai ke liye Mukhija Mandir takin diya ga.
